text.autoconfig.forager_bow_ench.title: Forager Bow Enchantment Settings
If true, Forager I will teleport XP. If false, teleport Items instead.
If true, Forager will be possible to get from Enchanting Tables. If false, it will not.
Forager Available For Enchanted Book Offer
If true, Forager will be possible to get from Enchanted Book Offers. If false, it will not.
If true, Forager will be possible to get from End City Chests. If false, it will not.
If true, the mod will print important debug events to the MC Log.
